== Standard Upgrade vs Release Upgrade ==

This procedure is for every day upgrading of Qubes-Whonix and will not perform a [[Release Upgrade]].

{{Release Upgrade}}

Before applying a release upgrade, it is useful to first complete a standard upgrade in both the <code>{{whonix-gw}}</code> and <code>{{whonix-ws}}</code> TemplateVMs, via Konsole:

* <code>Qubes App Menu(blue/grey "Q")</code> -> <code>Template: {{whonix-gw}}</code> -> <code>Konsole</code>
* <code>Qubes App Menu(blue/grey "Q")</code> -> <code>Template: {{whonix-ws}}</code> -> <code>Konsole</code>

Then perform the [[#Standard_Upgrade_Steps|Standard Upgrade Steps]] below in both terminals.

